OL,3,CThousands of fans celebrate the life
OL,4,Cof boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FThousands of fans packed Manchester's
OL,7,FAO Arena on 7 June to celebrate the
OL,8,Flife of Ricky Hatton at a Las Vegas-
OL,9,Fthemed tribute night.
OL,11,FStars from sport and showbiz came
OL,12,Ftogether to raise funds for the Ricky
OL,13,FHatton Foundation, which supports
OL,14,Fthose battling mental health issues.
OL,16,FThe 46 year old was found dead at his
OL,17,Fhome in Hyde in September 2025.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G1/8
