PN,39102
SC,0002
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780949162
OL,3,CThousands of fans celebrate the life
OL,4,Cof boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FRicky had spoken openly about his
OL,7,Fstruggles with his mental health. At
OL,8,Fan inquest in March 2026 a coroner
OL,9,Fruled he could not be satisfied that
OL,10,Fthe boxer had intended to take his own
OL,11,Flife.
OL,13,FEvening4Ricky featured a reimagined
OL,14,Fboxing stage as a line-up of artists
OL,15,Fand performers came out as part of a
OL,16,Fseries of 12 entertainment 'rounds' at
OL,17,Fthe arena where Ricky fought 15 of his
OL,18,Ffights, including his legendary
OL,19,Fvictory over Kostya Tszyu in June 2005.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
