PN,39103
SC,0003
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780949162
OL,3,CThousands of fans celebrate the life
OL,4,Cof boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FAmong those celebrating the Manchester
OL,7,Ficon were darts legend Phil Taylor,
OL,8,Fcomedian and TV presenter Paddy
OL,9,FMcGuinness, and former boxer Tony
OL,10,FBellew.
OL,12,FPaddy McGuinness said: "Ricky's one of
OL,13,Fthose people who transcends sport
OL,14,Freally, he was loved by everyone.
OL,16,F"I've been in various situations with
OL,17,Fhim over the years, and I couldn't not
OL,18,Fbe here tonight."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G3/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
