OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39104
SC,0004
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780949162
OL,3,CThousands of fans celebrate the life
OL,4,Cof boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FHe said: "I don't even think of Ricky
OL,7,Fas not being here, I still feel as
OL,8,Fthough he's here.
OL,10,F"It will be sad out there, but
OL,11,Fthere'll be a lot of laughter as well,
OL,12,Fand that's what he'd want."
OL,14,FFormer world champion boxer Tony
OL,15,FBellew said: "I've got so much
OL,16,Fadmiration and respect for Rick, I
OL,17,Floved him and adored him."
OL,19,FHe added: "You have to understand what
OL,20,FRick's meant to my sport and what he's
OL,21,Fdone to it.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G4/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
OL,23,TppppppppppppppppppGsource: itv.com/news
OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39105
SC,0005
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780949162
OL,3,CThousands of fans celebrate the life
OL,4,Cof boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,6,F"He literally revolutionised the sport
OL,7,Fat one stage. Never will it be seen
OL,8,Fagain - 30,000 people travelled over
OL,9,Fto Vegas when only 10,000 could get in
OL,10,Fthe stadium, and that tells you all
OL,11,Fyou need to know about Ricky Hatton."
OL,13,FAnd former boxer Anthony Crolla said:
OL,14,F"I say it all the time just like the
OL,15,Fsong, there was only one Ricky Hatton
OL,16,Fand anyone who was lucky enough to be
OL,17,Fhere for some of his big nights will
OL,18,Fagree."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G5/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
