OL,24,ANext Page BNW Eng NewsCThis Day FReg TV
FL,392,390,120,260,000,100
PN,39106
SC,0006
CT,2,C
PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780949162
OL,3,CThousands of fans celebrate the life
OL,4,Cof boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FRicky's brother Matthew Hatton said:
OL,7,F"He had so many great nights here, I
OL,8,Fdon't think anyone's lit up the place
OL,9,Flike he did here. Great memories."
OL,11,F"It's really nice to see so many
OL,12,Ffamiliar faces that I've not seen for
OL,13,Fso long ... it's going to be an
OL,14,Femotional night, but I'm looking
OL,15,Fforward to it."
OL,17,FManchester rapper Bugzy Malone
OL,18,Fperformed at the Evening4Ricky
OL,19,Fcelebration.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G6/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
