PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780949162
OL,3,CThousands of fans celebrate the life
OL,4,Cof boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,6,FHe said he took up boxing because he
OL,7,Fwas inspired by Ricky Hatton. "I think
OL,8,Fthe discipline of boxing changed my
OL,9,Flife undoubtedly."
OL,11,FBugzy Malone was joined by Campbell
OL,12,FHatton on stage for the song he
OL,13,Fdedicated to Ricky called 'The Hitman'.
OL,15,F"I thought what's important here is
OL,16,Fthat I address Campbell direct and let
OL,17,Fhim know that the city loves him and
OL,18,Fsupports him in whatever he does.
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G7/8
OL,2,W/*%+.-' "-$/*%+.!+,*%/*%/*-'T(,,,,,,,,,
