PS,c008
OL,0,        ECIMSBWebfax 1   F391A1780949162
OL,3,CThousands of fans celebrate the life
OL,4,Cof boxer Ricky Hatton
OL,6,F"He shouldn't feel the pressure in
OL,7,Fhaving to follow in his father's
OL,8,Ffootsteps."
OL,10,FHe added: "I wanted the family to come
OL,11,Faway from tonight feeling respected
OL,12,Fand loved."
OL,1,W~k4j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G8/8
